description:
TextEffects

A bunch of fun text effects, featuring mockify and Zalgo.

*Effects:*
bend
bubble
clap
flip
mirror
mock
owo (Thanks beerpiss!)
tiny capitals
zalgo
emojipasta (Thanks beerpiss!) (Emoji mappings provided by Kevin Galligan)

To use the effects:
They are simply slash commands, ex: /mock this is a demonstration
 
*this is basically a merger of mockify and Zalgo + more*

Download: https://github.com/FierysDiscordAddons/TextEffects/releases/download/v1.1.0/TextEffects.js
Source: https://github.com/FierysDiscordAddons/TextEffects
